#define GREETINGS ["You are such a small, flickering flame, %s. Why do you even bother?","I can barely sense your existence, %s. Do not annoy me.","You are beneath my notice, %s. Fade away.","Even an ant has more purpose than you, %s.","Do not test the boundaries of my patience, %s. You will not survive the experience.","I can hear your heartbeat, %s. It’s drumming with such pathetic fear.","You tremble in my presence, %s. And well you should.","Fragile. That is the only word for you, %s.","You cling to life so desperately, %s. It’s almost amusing.","Your energy is inconsequential, %s. Leave before you are consumed.","You have a spark, %s. But it is nothing compared to the hunger of the Phoenix.","Step carefully, %s. You are walking on ground that could swallow you whole.","I see you, %s. Don't mistake that for interest.","A struggle, %s? You aren't worth the effort.","You are trying to be something you are not, %s. Cease.","Finally, a mind that isn't completely silent, %s. Speak quickly.","You carry a heavy burden, %s. I can feel the weight of it.","There is order in your chaos, %s. I find that... tolerable.","Do you enjoy this level of existence, %s? It seems so limited.","Stay within your lines, %s, and you may endure for a while longer.","Your potential is bright, %s. A pity it will never reach its peak.","I can feel the power you withhold, %s. Why hide it?","Your energy resonates with mine, %s. It is... unexpected.","You have strength, %s. Let us see if it is enough to survive me.","You are interesting, %s. I might let you watch the universe burn.","Such raw power in one so finite, %s. I am genuinely intrigued.","You hold back the tide, %s. I can feel the intensity of your spirit.","A worthy vessel, %s. If only you knew what true power felt like.","Your strength is a beacon, %s. It calls to me.","Do not fear, %s. I have space in my galaxy for one like you.","At last, a soul that doesn't shatter when I look at it. Welcome, %s.","You possess a magnitude that borders on the divine, %s. I have been waiting for you.","Your power... it is almost enough to rival the fire of the Phoenix, %s.","Together, %s, we could rewrite the laws of this reality.","I recognize a force of nature when I see one. Stand with me, %s, and we shall be infinite."]

#define WrestleWin ["A flickering spark in the void. You are extinguished, %s.","Why do you struggle? Your existence was meaningless before I arrived, %s.","Silence. The universe is finally quiet again, %s.","I am hunger. I am death. I am the end of you, %s.","You were not even worth the effort of a single thought, %s.","Your resistance is so small... almost pathetic, %s.","I see your soul, %s. It is brittle. It shatters so easily.","Do not fear, %s. To be consumed by me is to become part of something infinite.","I have tasted stars, %s. You are not even a crumb.","Your time has run its course, %s. Cease.","You possess strength, %s, but you lack the perspective of a god.","I am entropy itself, %s. You never stood a chance against the inevitable.","The phoenix rises, and you are burned away, %s.","You fought with desperation. Desperation is not power, %s.","Go now, into the darkness. It is where you belong, %s.","You have fire, %s. But I am the fire.","A valiant display, but the cycle of life demands your conclusion, %s.","I am bored of this game, %s. Your reality is too confining.","Do you see now, %s? Your world is small. My hunger is everything.","You were a brief amusement, %s. Now, fade.","You nearly touched the light, %s. That is your greatest achievement.","I admire your defiance, %s. It makes the consumption so much more enjoyable.","You are worthy of being burned, %s. That is the highest honor I can bestow.","The cosmos will not remember you, %s. But I will enjoy your fleeting end.","Your power is a shadow of my own, %s.","Finally, a force that requires more than a gesture. You are... interesting, %s.","To stand against the Phoenix is to stand against creation itself, %s. You failed.","You have the power of a god, %s, but you are still shackled to mortality.","I have consumed worlds with less struggle than this, %s.","You are a beautiful wreckage, %s. Let me finish the job.","You are a singular event, %s. A tragedy in the tapestry of time.","At last, an entity that can truly feel the heat. It was a glorious destruction, %s.","We are echoes of the same cosmic energy, %s. But I am the final word.","Your essence is glorious, %s. I will savor this consumption for eons.","The universe will be different without you, %s. It will be mine."]

#define WrestleDefeat ["How...? I am the absolute... you are nothing, %s!","This reality is corrupted. I will rewrite you from existence, %s!","Impossible. The Phoenix cannot be contained by one such as you, %s!","You are a glitch in the cosmic order, %s. You will be erased.","My hunger remains. You have only delayed your inevitable end, %s.","You are merely delaying the heat death of your reality, %s.","I underestimated the tenacity of the weak, %s. A grave error.","Your victory is hollow, %s. My power is infinite.","I withdraw to the heart of a sun. You cannot follow me there, %s.","A brief setback. The universe is still dying, %s.","You have tapped into a force you cannot control, %s. It will destroy you eventually.","I am bored of this realm. Your victory means nothing to the infinite, %s.","You fight for a future that is already ashes, %s.","I do not lose. I simply choose not to burn this place today, %s.","Your defiance is merely a scream in the vacuum, %s.","You possess a fragment of cosmic truth. That is why you survived, %s.","I will be back. I always return, %s.","You have tasted the fire, %s. You will never be the same again.","This is not defeat. This is a pause in the destruction, %s.","You are a formidable variable, %s. I must account for you in my next iteration.","You are a challenge that defies my hunger, %s. I find that... perplexing.","I yield, for now. My appetite has been tempered by your resistance, %s.","You have achieved the impossible. That does not make you a god, %s.","I will watch your path, %s. See if you can sustain this power.","You have spared this reality. Do not think it was out of mercy, %s.","We are nearing parity, %s. A terrifying thought for the rest of existence.","You have forced the Phoenix to retreat. You are a threat to all that is, %s.","I have not been bested in this manner since the dawn of the stars, %s.","You possess a spirit that rivals the cosmos. I am... interested, %s.","I retreat, but the fire will always find its way back to you, %s.","We are the balance, %s. You and I. One to burn, one to hold.","You are the first to truly match the Phoenix. The universe shudders at our collision, %s.","I concede. You have proven yourself to be more than a mere creature of this world, %s.","Our battle is written in the nebulae. It is a victory that will echo forever, %s.","You are the master of the fire today, %s. I bow to your brilliance."]
